entry.title: MARBLE ANKLE STRAPS
entry.summary:
Vendor: SuzieB Fitness
Type: Ankle Straps
Price: 25.00

Includes one pair of ankle straps.

Use these ankle straps on the cable machine. The first part you'll notice is how different and more comfortable these are than most of the ones out there. No more borrowing the used ankle straps from the gym. Enjoy your workouts more with a cushioned lining, a secure way to tighten the straps, and a stylish design on these marble ankle straps!

The ankle straps feature a SuzieB logo on the front rubber label and come in a printed poly bag. Check Instagram for Suzie's videos to see how it is used.
